headline: Stryker to participate in the Bank of America Securities 2025 Global Healthcare Conference
summary: Portage, Michigan, April 29, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Stryker (NYSE:SYK) will participate in the Bank of America Securities 2025 Global Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, May 13, 2025, at the Encore at Wynn Hotel in Las Vegas, Nevada. Representing the company will be Preston Wells, Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, and Jason Beach, Vice President, Finance and Investor Relations.
